result.formatted_address: 2 Dundas St, Mong Kok, Hong Kong
result.name: Yuet Lai Shun

reviews.text:
Friendly and efficient Cantonese restaurant.
It was interesting to note that they had been awarded a Michelin Bib Gourmand accolade - fully deserved from my point of view.

Service was very fast (almost too fast), and our waiter charming  and very helpful.

Food on the whole was excellent, fresh, from an eclectic menu, both in Chinese and English.

Well worth a visit.

Occupying a corner lot, this bright and airy restaurant offers old school Cantonese dishes with incredibly warm and friendly service. The almond milk double boiled soup was very flavorful and was the highlight of the meal. Meanwhile the 小炒皇 (Cantonese stir fried) with Chives blossom and a variety of seafood was also good but I would have liked it even more if the dish came out drier. The steamed crab on a bed of glutenous rice was also good as you can see the crab was full of crab roe. Again would have liked it a little more of the rice was quite as wet. Reservation is recommended as this place is rather popular after it was included in HK Michelin guide.

Sorry to say I don't see why this restaurant can get Michellin star.  The fried squid is horrible, the dual color chicken and pork lung soup are nothing special, the roast pork stir noodles has soda power favour and the fried veggie is too oily.  Paying over $1,000 for such quality of food then can really forget about it.  The Eagle Nest at next door hotel is much better in my own view.
Food was good, service a little average. Served us tea without asking and then charged more than I would have expected.

Food wasn’t that bad, but not that great either - definitely overrated; don’t understand how this could be on the Michelin guide. If you’re a foreigner, staff will hand you a menu in English/Korean, but prices on this menu are higher than the local Cantonese one. Staff seems to ignore non-local customers.

result.adr_address: 香港旺角登打士街2號
result.name: 粵來順

reviews.text: 東西難吃，價錢貴，價格不明確有點亂來的感覺，菜也出錯了，一盤牛肉炒菜裡面牛肉只有三四片，還每一個人都要收喝茶錢

普通到極，完全唔值呢個價！
可以讚的是侍應有禮，冇黑面人。
多款特色菜，值得嘗試。
為杏汁豬肺湯而來。雖然在某飲食網站評價平平，可是完全滿意當日的服務。豬肺湯好多料，好鮮甜。其他小菜碟頭相當大，人數少就兩三味已非常足夠。價錢並不便宜但有機會會和朋友再試。
米芝蓮當然有保將啦
